ing: 2 (12.5 fl oz) cans white meat chicken
des: "A delicious combination of tacos and Buffalo chicken dip. Leave in the slow cooker longer for stronger flavor. Serve with tortilla chips, celery, carrots, or on taco shells."
ins:
Mix chicken, Cheddar cheese, Greek yogurt, taco sauce, taco seasoning mix, and ranch dressing mix in a slow cooker.
Cook on Low until warmed through, about 30 minutes.
